- [ ] `tournament_state()` partitions group-stage matches into `played` vs `remaining_group_fixtures` (by `status`) and carries the 12-group `standings`
- [ ] Knockout matches with `null` teams parse to `home_team is None` / `away_team is None` (no crash); all non-null names pass through `normalize_team`
- [ ] Pydantic value objects `LiveMatch`, `GroupStanding`, `TournamentState` with `ConfigDict(extra="ignore")`
